OL,3,CTwo men in hospital after 'fighting
OL,4,Cwith weapons' following car crash
OL,6,FTwo men have been taken to hospital
OL,7,Fafter "fighting with weapons"
OL,8,Ffollowing a car crash in Coventry.
OL,10,FThe crash involved two cars and
OL,11,Fhappened in Wyken - near the junction
OL,12,Fof Sewell Highway and Ansty Road -
OL,13,Fshortly before 4am on Friday.
OL,15,FThe two people have "potentially
OL,16,Fserious" injuries, though they are not
OL,17,Fbelieved to be life-threatening.
OL,19,FPolice are still trying to trace one
OL,20,Fof the cars and have shared a
OL,21,Fdescription.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
