OL,3,CTwo men in hospital after 'fighting
OL,4,Cwith weapons' following car crash
OL,6,FA West Midlands Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're in the early stages of
OL,8,Four investigation to establish exactly
OL,9,Fwhat has happened and who was involved.
OL,11,F"We understand one of the vehicles
OL,12,Finvolved was a white Kia Sorento which
OL,13,Fsustained damage before making off,
OL,14,Fand we're trying to locate this car.
OL,16,F"A scene is currently in place while
OL,17,Four enquiries continue and we remain
OL,18,Fkeen to hear from anyone with
OL,19,Finformation."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
